<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.5.7">
<l>niṟainta vaṉpaḻi naṅkuṭikkiva ḷeṉṟaṉṉai kāṇakkoṭāḷ</l>
<l>ciṟantakīrttit tirukku ṟuṅkuṭi nampiyai nāṉkaṇṭapiṉ</l>
<l>ṉiṟaintacōti veḷḷañ cūḻnta nīṇṭapoṉ mēṉiyoṭu</l>
<l>niṟainteṉ ṉuḷḷē niṉṟoḻintā ṉēmiyaṅ kaiyuḷatē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>“Full strong blame she [is] to our familiy”, so mother doesn’t let [me be] seen.</l>
<l>After I saw Nampi of Tirukkuṟuṅkuṭi with excellent fame,</l>
<l>he stayed behind inside me who is full [his] tall golden body</l>
<l>surrounded by a flood of full light and of the discus that is in [his] palm.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
